Data Collection Method: Jamar Count Board (Unit # D4-4240)
1) Lockhart Elementary School is located less than 1 mile from the
studied intersection and was in session on the date of the count,
as were all Wake County Schools.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted – none were disabled.
3) NB approach grade is 1% and EB & WB is 0%.
4) No highway construction was observed within a ¼ mile radius.
5) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
6) Counter took breaks from 1:15 – 1:45 PM and 4:30 – 5:00 PM.
Data for these periods was interpolated.
7) The counter did not have any additional notes.
